caption: I don't really know what to think about this place. I deeply like Islamic cultures but I feel like they don't make enough efforts to cross cultures and build more dialogues. I always enjoy every event I see there though. For a new building like that they could take care of their toilets. That's a basic.
The staff, the building and the curation of the Islamic contemporary artworks are fantastic. Thank you so much for your kindness and generosity.
Be early if you want to get in. It‚Äôs always full. Good facilities and clean place.
great place to visit, not only for Muslims but with any religious belief
Nice cultural centre, art gallery and it has a small mosque
Strange place, between religion and secularism. There is a prayer room on first floor.

Pleasant exhibition at ICI on the transmission of traditions The establishment has a courtyard with a stage

Nothing to say, it's just perfect! The entire staff is lovely and helpful. The patio is spacious, comfortable and re. Very affordable prices. And the icing on the cake is the always interesting and free exhibitions.

Necessary institution in the most exciting district of Paris It opens late, at noon, before you have to walk around the neighborhood and watch the people in the streets Arab restaurant made of love in the institute Not to forget the next time you go to Paris

We came to see the exhibition From calligraphy to street art and had a very nice time. Super welcoming and pleasant staff. Only mini problem: the exhibition was very (too) short but on the other hand very beautiful.

I visited for the first time, very nice, there are two buildings, they also used the Hamamme space also for exhibitions... nice setting, full of potential... top staff. I really liked this place, the only problem is the neighborhood, it's very busy and especially not easy to get home at night.

Atypical and little-known place, but very nice: spacious indoor terrace bar (too bad the service is very slow), with a superb graffiti fresco. Exhibition space on two buildings offering varied settings. Exhibition: Beirut is very interesting.
Very nice place to relax or taste oriental specialties
Small, very relevant exhibition and a restaurant with a warm welcome and exceptional value for money, in a very pleasant setting despite the rain :)

It is a shame to indicate on the website that the exhibitions continue at another address if it is to be received and learn that in fact this is absolutely not the case. Disappointed to have come for nothing, I really wanted to go‚Ä¶

Coming to ICI for a culinary workshop (very good in fact), I took the opportunity to discover the current exhibition on calligraphy. Bright and pleasant place. Regarding the toilets, it's true that they didn't seem clean to me. To see again. I will come back to this place for organized events and exhibitions.
I came to the mosque and it is beautiful and the people in it are good
An interesting place for lovers of Islam from different cultures. I give it a 4 because there is nowhere to wash your hands... In such and such an unstable time! It exists, but it was closed.
The hives of Paris very warm welcome with the facilitators of the honey making workshop

Pleasant places (2 sites for exhibitions, one with a restaurant/associative tea room with delicious food and low prices, friendly place, with large terrace... The exhibitions are always very interesting and free. Very friendly welcome. I warmly recommend!
Very nice place in the Goutte d'Or district and entry is free. This institute has the originality of being divided into two.
Very good, I recommend this place, beautiful exhibition and above all the dishes offered are so good, it invites us to travel and discover new flavors

A unique place where the magic of oriental tales and the scents of Maghreb spices combine!!! Recommended for those like me who are in search of culture and knowledge... The exhibition gallery is always rich and the restaurant will certainly take you on a journey without counting on the original shows and musical scenes in the evening... A change of scenery guaranteed !
